    "en": {
      "title": "Power cut at Prime Minister's house: Inquiry ordered",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Ratnayake, chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, has said that investigations are being carried out regarding the power cut in the area before Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe's house was set on fire.",
        "Yesterday (09) yesterday evening after 6 pm, when it was not decided to cut off the electricity in the said area, was this a planned operation? He mentioned that an investigation is being conducted in this regard. (a)"
      ],
